{"tid":1199058,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【短片】旺角警民者對峙 電筒閃燈互照射","createTime":"2019-06-10T11:32:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T11:56:31.000Z","uid":162866,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e13bc266b67a6186b6a207e3295f81253b7760ce","tid":1199058,"uid":162866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:32:50.000Z","msg":"強光能令被照射者昏眩，為執法部門常用技巧<br />\n<br />\n強光亦能阻礙攝影機正常運作，令拍得畫面嚗光不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2014/10/18<br />\n<br />\n回帶學野<br />\n<br />\n旺角自今凌晨始，警民通宵對峙至天亮。雙方對抗的方式連日層出不窮，除了雨傘對警棍，剪刀對索帶外，還有閃光燈對手電筒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n昨凌晨4時，警方與示威者在彌敦道與亞皆老街交界處爆發爭執，其間，有示威者用單反相機的外置閃光燈，向多名警員照射，警員則用打開手電筒作「光學還擊」。雙方各不相讓，一度僵持，警員不停大聲命令示威者停止照射。其後，有其他示威者勸止雙方，這場另類對抗才告終結。"},{"pid":"04dee71920b7b8567aaa531cb1a0b047e571c778","tid":1199058,"uid":162866,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:35:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GK3hGF6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGK3hGF6.jpg&h=306268c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢D可變焦閃光電筒鴨寮街唔洗100蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be02478a3c4bb4155989064c1de763bc593e00bd","tid":1199058,"uid":20174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"04dee71920b7b8567aaa531cb1a0b047e571c778","tid":1199058,"uid":162866,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:35:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GK3hGF6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGK3hGF6.jpg&h=306268c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢D可變焦閃光電筒鴨寮街唔洗100蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:36:27.000Z","msg":"有啲電筒又支警棍咁長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dc9704cc6fa15eaf0a2216f8d5851240a6c9da6","tid":1199058,"uid":162866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:3